             was indicted for <rs id="t17631207-30-off167" type="offenceDescription">
                     <interp inst="t17631207-30-off167" type="offenceCategory" value="theft"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17631207-30-off167" type="offenceSubcategory" value="theftFromPlace"></interp>
               stealing one cloth coat, value 10 s. one cloth waistcoat, value 10 s. two India dimity waistcoats, and one ruffle-shirt, the property of 
                     
                        <persName id="t17631207-30-victim295" type="victimName">
                           Samuel 
                           Jackman 
                        <interp inst="t17631207-30-victim295" type="surname" value="Jackman"></interp>
